text: The 1976 Navy Midshipmen football team represented the United States Naval Academy (USNA) during the 1976 NCAA Division I football season. Navy competed as an independent with no conference affiliation. The team was led by fourth- year head coach George Welsh. ==Schedule== ==Personnel== ==References== Navy Midshipmen Category:Navy Midshipmen football seasons Navy
